{"tid":390714,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"ive個廚藝學園好撚伏","createTime":"2017-09-07T09:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T12:05:41.000Z","uid":93905,"like":294,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5389813023b84ff37a40e6e24fc4b0ca767aa155","tid":390714,"uid":93905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"先唔講薄扶林有幾撚遠<br />\n入到去勁撚多理論堂<br />\n一個星期冇幾多次入廚房<br />\n仲要一返到去就要換到廚師制服<br />\n你老味全日都唔撚入廚房淨係坐班房<br />\n咁都要換衫 有病架?<br />\n最搞笑係係學校入邊見到任何人都要打招呼<br />\n我屌你老母唔撚識你都要同你打招呼<br />\n大專黎架屌你 d規矩搞到好似做返小學生咁<br />\n我小學個陣係學校見到d三鳩唔識七個d老師都唔會叫佢啦<br />\n打你老母飛機咩<br />\nmiss又要叫madam<br />\n上堂玩手機訓教都要俾人照肺<br />\n又要掛撚住張學生證係心口<br />\n<br />\n好彩我今日quit撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5239c6d074e6e8b19d3cdea58cbb6d0038d33b","tid":390714,"uid":95378,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"好過中國廚藝訓練學院"},{"pid":"fe7ee80c1e12ac9c34be627a60bde5783ac1181d","tid":390714,"uid":78385,"like":61,"dislike":5,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好過中國廚藝訓練學院</blockquote><br />\n佢咪講緊 中國廚藝訓練學院 囉！"},{"pid":"9fa5bca691fe99205e02ae7723fa21bca93d9888","tid":390714,"uid":46454,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好過中國廚藝訓練學院</blockquote><br />\n佢咪講緊 中國廚藝訓練學院 囉！</blockquote><br />\n樓上應該係講緊食神套戲入面ge&quot;中國廚藝訓練學院&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296cddc0eb0c6aa9cace776cdd280eef5119f07a","tid":390714,"uid":79953,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"得罪方丈，仲想走"},{"pid":"6e9ab395788c3b891af46c2c4571ddb3962549b9","tid":390714,"uid":29523,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"I大十八銅人？"},{"pid":"f6c59e9306ecd31864ec390be42170030476b912","ti